OL,3,CPeter Murrell expected in court on
OL,4,Cembezzlement charges
OL,6,FFormer SNP chief executive Peter
OL,7,FMurrell is due to appear in court for
OL,8,Fa preliminary hearing, as he faces
OL,9,Fcharges of embezzling more than
OL,10,F#459,000 from the party.
OL,12,FHe is expected to appear at the High
OL,13,FCourt in Edinburgh for a hearing which
OL,14,Fhad originally been scheduled to take
OL,15,Fplace in Glasgow in February.
OL,17,FMurrell is accused of embezzling the
OL,18,Ffunds from the party between August
OL,19,F2010 and January 2023, according to an
OL,20,Findictment seen by the Press
OL,21,FAssociation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/3
