OL,3,CPeter Murrell expected in court on
OL,4,Cembezzlement charges
OL,6,FThe 61-year-old, who is Nicola
OL,7,FSturgeon's estranged husband, is
OL,8,Falleged to have used the money to buy
OL,9,Fitems including a motorhome and luxury
OL,10,Fgoods, and towards the purchase of two
OL,11,Fcars.
OL,13,FHe was first arrested in April 2023 as
OL,14,Fpart of the police investigation into
OL,15,Fthe SNP's finances and was charged in
OL,16,FApril 2024.
OL,18,FHe appeared at Edinburgh Sheriff Court
OL,19,Fin March 2025, where he faced a charge
OL,20,Fof embezzlement, making no plea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/3
