OL,3,CPeter Murrell expected in court on
OL,4,Cembezzlement charges
OL,6,FThe indictment includes allegations
OL,7,Fthat in 2020, Murrell used party funds
OL,8,Fto buy a #124,550 motorhome for his
OL,9,Fown personal use.
